<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Availability">Availability</span></h2>
<p>The Heavy Nemesis is available at two <a href="/index.php/Paranid_Shipyard" title="Paranid Shipyard">Paranid Shipyards</a> for around 14 million credits, which is about average for this type of ship. If purchase is not an option, they are often found escorting Paranid warships or in patrol groups and can be boarded.  It rarely goes unescorted.
</p>
