<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Suggested_Roles">Suggested Roles</span></h2>
<p>A highly versatile craft in combat, the Heavy Nemesis can lead sector patrols with a fighter escort.  It is also fast enough to keep up with almost all frigates and other battleships, so is effective as an escort.  However, its cramped cargo bay prevents it from being useful as a player ship.
</p>
